  "system": {
    "biography": {
      "value": "<p>Pebble Sprites are scouts and minor nuisances. Their Tremorsense within 10 feet tells the summoner what is moving on any surface they occupy, and their minor stone shaping is occasionally exactly what is needed. A summoner who calls one for a fight has made a conceptual error. One called to monitor a floor, plug a small gap, or confirm whether something is approaching through ground vibration will find it performs that task adequately.</p>"
