    "sensesNotes": "Darkvision 60 ft, Tremorsense 10 ft",
    "tactics": "",
    "attacksNotes": "<ul>\n<li><strong>Gravel Hurl [Combat]:</strong> Ranged attack (Dex 2 + Ranged Combat 1), Range: 20 ft\n<ul>\n<li><em>Margin 1:</em> 2 damage</li>\n<li><em>Margin 2:</em> 2 damage; target makes Reflex save (1 success) or gains Dazzled condition until end of their next turn from gravel in the eyes</li>\n</ul></li>\n</ul>",
    "specialAbilitiesNotes": "<ul>\n<li><strong>Earth Sense:</strong> Aware of all vibrations through the ground within 10 ft. Cannot be surprised by creatures touching the same surface.</li>\n<li><strong>Stone Shape (minor):</strong> Once per encounter, alters a small quantity of loose stone — fills a crack up to 1 inch wide and 3 feet long, creates a rough step in soft stone, or dislodges a pebble from height to drop on a target below (1 damage, requires height advantage).</li>\n</ul>",
